Claudine Komgang-Fotsing (amụrụ n'abalị iri abụọ na otu n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1974) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba ọsọ lara ezumike nká bụ onye ọkachamara na mita 400.
O meriri nrite ọla edo na afọ 2000 African Championships
O mekwara asọmpi na afọ 1999 World Championships na afọ 2000 Summer Olympics n'erughị nke ikpeazụ.
Oge kachasị mma ya bụ 50.73 sekọnd, nke o nwetara na Julaị, na afọ 2000 na Mexico City.
